# Skill Routing Policy

Local skill catalog (example paths):
- `.cursor/skills/awesome-skills/systematic-debugging`
- `.cursor/skills/awesome-skills/verification-before-completion`
- `.cursor/skills/awesome-skills/agent-memory-mcp`
- `.cursor/skills/awesome-skills/agent-memory-systems`

Routing rules:
1. Bug/regression tasks -> apply `systematic-debugging` first.
2. Completion claims -> apply `verification-before-completion` with fresh evidence.
3. Long-running tasks -> apply memory skills and synchronize memories.
4. Invariant-sensitive changes -> enforce `project_config.md` + assumption guard.
